Mr. Lotoc. We have Atty. Van Angluben, the then Executive Officer for Operations ng 
Cybercrime Division; Atty. Vanessa Asuncion, the Executive Officer for Administration back then; 
John Mark Calilung, the agent of case; and myself, Your Honor.

Mr. Ligutan. Now, you mentioned Atty. Lotoc, iyong four stages ng Cybercrime Division 
for the information ng ating honorable judges at saka iyong publiko. This is the question now: 
ano ba iyong four stages ng investigation na ito?
